Package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.attributes

Interface Radioactive

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItemAttribute
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RadioactiveItem

    public interface Radioactive
extends ItemAttribute
    This Interface, when attached to a class that inherits from SlimefunItem, marks the Item as radioactive. Carrying such an item will give the wearer the radiation effect. You can specify a level of Radioactivity for the severity of the effect.
    Author:
    TheBusyBiscuit

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      Radioactivity getRadioactivity​()
      This method returns the level of Radioactivity for this Radioactive item.

    • Method Detail

      • getRadioactivity

        Radioactivity getRadioactivity​()
        This method returns the level of Radioactivity for this Radioactive item. Higher levels cause more severe radiation effects.
        Returns:
        The level of Radioactivity of this item.
